{
  "stem": "15694.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Anyway, the next one, prisoners, yeah, the reason for his hanging was said to be as he was whistling the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And somebody else-- I'm sure we just-- either the film or somewhere else I heard they was whistling 'The Communist Internationale.' Whatever it was, it was for whistling that he was hanged.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the other person, whatever he did, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I only remember the name was given as [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we had a friend-- my family had a friend of that name in Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I looked at the man, but it wasn't him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Maybe a relation, maybe his brothers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But he already was dead, dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was-- his hands were tied around the back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I don't know how he killed himself, but he was dead.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But since the judgement was to be hanged, he was hanged.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then to finish the macabre show, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] a smaller SS man, and he was leaning back to, to look taller, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He leaned back so far that it really looked ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then pulled-- nonchalantly, he pulled a, a revolver, and shot the two hanging people, a bullet, you know, under the chin.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a jerk and a movement, and that was the end, surely.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as I say, a, a picture-- a suitable end to a macabre show.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now what comes next?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] another time we were called.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, at this time, actually, I, I, I frantically thought if I could write these things down, I wanted to start my book then-- a book then, a-- some kind of a diary.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I had no pen and no paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I remember that it took me afterwards over 40 years to write my book.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
